race.comment: LYN'S BIANCA (1) is a talented type who notched her 15th career success when too good (30.58) at this track last time. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Will go close again if runs up to latest. AUNTY MEEKA (8) goes very well here starting 14 times for five wins and six minors. Below best last time at The Meadows (30.59) in a Grade 5 FIN, finishing a 8 length sixth. Looks one of the chances. ELITE DOM (3) boasts a strong record this journey with 13 wins and 12 minors from 33 tries. Missed the frame latest (31.53) when eighth over 525m at this track in a NG. Can feature with the right run. QUEEN OF SPADES (2) can sneak into the finish.

Live2.SchedulerNote: P2 Country AUD $2,490 Switch to Wagga R8 - 30secs out from start time. Switch back Enhanced after race
